      "comment": "SKYHIGH ADDA (5) resumes after showing good promise last time in, placing in her first two outings including the Group 1 Westbred Classic before heading to the paddock off a Gloucester Park win from a wider barrier than this in October. Has upside and looks very well placed for a winning return. IN FULL FLIGHT (6) returns having only once missed the placings in a four-start maiden campaign that was highlighted by a win from this barrier at Gloucester Park along with a close-up placing behind SKYHIGH ADDA. A recent trial win should have her ready to go. LIVY ANN (8) comes off a maiden win last time out at Pinjarra. Draws for a trail so can be competitive again along with LADY CRUNCH TIME (4) who has progressed nicely this time in, culminating in a breakthrough win from this barrier last start at Northam.",
